                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>So we did. We went to Cookout. Take that, hipsters.</p>
<p>As amazing as my banana pudding shake was, though, it wasn't enough to get me off the slow boat to boredville.</p>
<p>So here I sit, pondering, disappointed that I have so little left to discover at Duke. I just wish, for once, the routine would change and I could convince myself that Duke had much more left in store for me.</p>
<p>Wait, there's a Panda Express on the Plaza?</p>
<p>Maybe I haven't figured it out after all.</p>
<p>Meeting adjourned.</p>
<p>THE CHAIRMAN doesn't mind that his BBQ pork has 1570 milligrams of sodium. I mean, it has at least 1571 milligrams of taste.</p>
